methods.comment: * Version of {@link #onCreateView(String, Context, AttributeSet)} * that also supplies the parent that the view created view will be * placed in. * * @param parent The parent that the created view will be placed * in; note that this may be null. * @param name Tag name to be inflated. * @param context The context the view is being created in. * @param attrs Inflation attributes as specified in XML file. * * @return View Newly created view. Return null for the default * behavior.
